📘 ACTIVITY PLANNING
👉 Meaning:
“Project ke kaam (activities) ko plan, order aur time ke according arrange karna”

📌 1. Project Schedule

👉 Schedule = Kaam kab start aur kab finish hoga
✔ Includes:
Task list
Start time
End time
Deadlines
🎯 Example:
UI Design → 3 days
Backend → 7 days
Testing → 2 days

👉 Simple:
“Project ka timetable”

📌 2. Sequencing and Scheduling Activities

👉 Sequencing = Kaun sa kaam pehle aur kaun baad me
👉 Scheduling = Kaam kab hoga

🎯 Example:
Design → pehle
Development → baad me
Testing → last

👉 Simple:
“Kaam ka order + timing fix karna”

📌 3. Network Planning Models

👉 Diagram use karke project plan karna
✔ Types:
PERT (Program Evaluation Review Technique)
CPM (Critical Path Method)

👉 Simple:
“Graph/diagram se project flow dikhana”

📌 4. Forward Pass

👉 Calculate karta hai:
“Earliest time kab activity start/finish hogi”

✔ Output:
ES = Earliest Start
EF = Earliest Finish

👉 Simple:
“Sabse jaldi kab kaam ho sakta hai”

📌 5. Backward Pass

👉 Calculate karta hai:
“Latest time kab tak kaam complete karna chahiye”

✔ Output:
LS = Latest Start
LF = Latest Finish

👉 Simple:
“Late hone se bachne ke liye max limit”

📌 6. Activity Float (Slack)

👉 Float = Extra time available

✔ Formula:
Float = LS - ES (ya LF - EF)

🎯 Example:
Activity delay ho sakti hai without affecting project

👉 Simple:
“Kitna delay allowed hai”

📌 7. Shortening Project Duration

👉 Project ko jaldi finish karna
✔ Methods:
Extra resources add karo
Overtime work
Parallel tasks

👉 Simple:
“Project fast complete karna”

📌 8. Activity on Arrow (AOA) Networks

👉 Diagram jisme:
Arrow = Activity
Circle (node) = Event

👉 Flow left → right
👉 Simple:

“Arrow se project activities show karna”

📌 9. Risk Management

👉 Meaning:
“Project ke risks identify, analyze aur control karna”

📌 10. Nature of Risk

👉 Risk ka nature:
Uncertain hota hai
Future me hota hai
Loss cause kar sakta hai

👉 Simple:
“Risk = uncertainty + possible loss”

📌 11. Types of Risk
🔹 Technical Risk
Technology fail
🔹 Financial Risk
Budget problem
🔹 Schedule Risk
Delay
🔹 Resource Risk
Team issue
🔹 External Risk
Market / legal issue

👉 Simple:
“Alag-alag type ke problems”

📌 12. Managing Risk

👉 Steps:
Identify risk
Analyze risk
Plan solution
Control risk

👉 Simple:
“Risk ko handle karna”

📌 13. Hazard Identification

👉 Hazard = Danger source
👉 Identify:

Kya galat ho sakta hai?
🎯 Example:
Server crash
Data loss

👉 Simple:
“Danger ko pehle se pehchanna”

📌 14. Hazard Analysis

👉 Analyze:
Risk kitna serious hai?
Kitni probability hai?

👉 Simple:
“Risk ki depth samajhna”

📌 15. Risk Planning and Control

👉 Plan:
Backup plan
Extra budget
Alternative solution

👉 Control:
Monitor risk
Reduce impact

👉 Simple:
“Risk ke liye ready rehna + control karna”

